2006-09-26 Tuesday 05:37  stronk7

	* db/install.xml: 
	
	Some notes:
	
	- Foreign keys are really cool (at the XMLDB Editor). Define them
	as necessary   as they allow as one "formal" structure of the DB.
	They won't cause problems   on generation, mainly because only the
	underlying index will be created.  - Please, put comments inside
	each table/field/key/index field, mainly because   XML comments
	will be deleted if the file is edited by - The XMLDB Editor. Please
	use it ;-) - Also, one unique index was wrong in the XML file,
	fixed now.

2006-09-26 Tuesday 01:49  sam_marshall

	* db/mysql.php: 
	
	change from UNIQUE KEY to UNIQUE INDEX

