	* view.php: 
	
	wiki: Fix for broken view on new (empty) wiki pages.
	
	The wiki should display the 'edit' screen when a user tries to view
	a page that doesn't exist. This output should not be filtered.
	
	Merged from MOODLE_16_STABLE
	
	Author: Donal McMullan

