2004-06-24 Thursday 23:56  mchurch

	* lib.php, mod.html, version.php, view.php, db/mysql.php,
	db/mysql.sql, ewiki/ewiki.php: 
	
	Added a per-wiki option to allow disabling of automatic camel case
	linking.  If pages have been created using camel case, and this
	option is activated, those pages remain, but may not be linkable.
	If the option is disabled, they will be linked again.

